{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/carbon-to-take-code-shots","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"3113cd74-ba61-5ee9-a57c-cd578189b87c","html":"<p>The developer community is constantly on the move and with it, the way everyone share and interact with each others code does too. <code class=\"language-text\">Carbon</code> is meant for that! The easiest way to create and share beautiful images of your code.</p>\n<p>Just head to <a href=\"https://carbon.now.sh/?bg=rgba(74%2C144%2C226%2C1)&#x26;t=material&#x26;wt=none&#x26;l=auto&#x26;ds=false&#x26;dsyoff=20px&#x26;dsblur=68px&#x26;wc=true&#x26;wa=true&#x26;pv=56px&#x26;ph=56px&#x26;ln=false&#x26;fm=Fira%20Code&#x26;fs=14px&#x26;lh=152%25&#x26;si=false&#x26;es=2x&#x26;wm=false&#x26;code=%252F%252Ftype%2520here\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Carbon</a> site and type your code in <code class=\"language-text\">//type here</code> section. Choose over theme, language and other settings. And Boom! its ready to be shared in a beautiful way.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/2eb79/carbon.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/8ac56/carbon.webp 240w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/d3be9/carbon.webp 480w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/e46b2/carbon.webp 960w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/c6aef/carbon.webp 1256w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/8ff5a/carbon.png 240w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/e85cb/carbon.png 480w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/d9199/carbon.png 960w,\n/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/2eb79/carbon.png 1256w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/decc3c2cecc189bae59c414ccc11184b/d9199/carbon.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>With Carbon, you can import from GitHub gist. Simply append a GitHub gist id to the url, e.g. <code class=\"language-text\">carbon.now.sh/&lt;GIST_ID_HERE&gt;</code>. Customize things like your image’s syntax theme, window style, and more. Save your image or Tweet a link with one click.</p>\n<p>The simple way to use it frequently is via your IDE, visit <a href=\"https://github.com/dawnlabs/carbon#community\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">community</a> section to integrate with your favorite IDE.\nI use it as VS Code extension to share the code. Simply highlighting my code and using command palette search as “carbon” does the work.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/daf70/carbon2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/8ac56/carbon2.webp 240w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/d3be9/carbon2.webp 480w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/e46b2/carbon2.webp 960w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/f992d/carbon2.webp 1440w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/882b9/carbon2.webp 1920w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/41fb3/carbon2.webp 2464w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/8ff5a/carbon2.png 240w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/e85cb/carbon2.png 480w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/d9199/carbon2.png 960w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/07a9c/carbon2.png 1440w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/29114/carbon2.png 1920w,\n/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/daf70/carbon2.png 2464w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/da9c7cf90124f66691dc68029fc5fbfe/d9199/carbon2.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>As I notice, with everything in URL, I believe the tool will fail on Internet Explorer, as it has URL length limit. Haven’t tested though! But that’s not a concern!</p>\n<p>Official Site: <a href=\"https://dawnlabs.io/carbon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Carbon</a></p>\n<p>Alternative: <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=pnp.polacode\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Polacode</a> This is for VS code editor embedded workflow. Provides same functionality as carbon.</p>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/carbon-to-take-code-shots","tagSlugs":["/tag/tools/","/tag/code/","/tag/ide/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-04-21T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Are you impressed by code screenshot that you see twitter and online? and wonder, which IDE theme are people using? or you want to share your professional awesome code screenshot with colleague? Here is the tool everyone is using! ","tags":["Tools","Code","IDE"],"title":"Admire beautiful images of your source code","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/carbon-to-take-code-shots"}}}